  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Location_map_Summer_Isles.svg\" class=\"image\" title=\"Red Flower Vale is located in Summer Isles\"><img alt=\"Red Flower Vale is located in Summer Isles\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/54/Location_map_Summer_Isles.svg/300px-Location_map_Summer_Isles.svg.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"298\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/54/Location_map_Summer_Isles.svg/450px-Location_map_Summer_Isles.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/54/Location_map_Summer_Isles.svg/600px-Location_map_Summer_Isles.svg.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 65.1%; left: 64.7%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -3px; top: -3px; width: 5px; font-size: 5px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/5px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Red Flower Vale\" width=\"5\" height=\"5\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/8px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/10px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: 0.5em; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\">Red Flower Vale</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">The <a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Isles\" title=\"Summer Isles\">Summer Isles</a> and the location of the Red Flower Vale\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>The <b>Red Flower Vale</b> is a settled river valley located in eastern <a href=\"/index.php/Jhala\" title=\"Jhala\">Jhala</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Isles\" title=\"Summer Isles\">Summer Isles</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiafthe_west.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiafthe_west.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiafthe_known_world.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiafthe_known_world.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Red_Flower_Vale&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The Red Flower Vale was the seat of Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Jalabhar_Xho\" title=\"Jalabhar Xho\">Jalabhar Xho</a> before he went into exile. He petitions the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a> every so often for the men to retake it, but is always put off.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Red_Flower_Vale&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiafthe_west.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiafthe_west.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i>, The West.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiafthe_known_world.7B.7B